    "en": {
      "title": "Chinese shipping issue: India ready to face challenges",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "India's Union Shipping Minister Sarbananda Sonowal has said that India is well prepared to deal with any challenges that may arise after Sri Lanka allowed the Chinese ship to dock in its territorial waters.",
        "Addressing the media in Chennai, the minister also said that under the dynamic leadership of Prime Minister Narendra Modi, India is ready to deal effectively with any kind of situation (a)"
      ],
